title: Wholesale Price of Haymowers, 5 Feet Regular Lift for United States
notes:
Series Is Presented Here As Two Variables--(1)--Original Data, 1913-1937 (2)--Original Data, 1933-1944. Data Are Prices For "Hay Mowers, 5 Foot Regular Lift, Factory" For Period 1913-1928. In 1929, The Series Is Called "Mower, Hay" But Prices Seem To Be Continuous (NBER Note). This Series Was Revised In 1938. See "Wholesale Prices," January, 1938, P.12. Source: 1913-1925 Data Are From Mimeographed Sheets From Bls. For 1926- 1937 Data, See Bls Bulletins And "Wholesale Prices."

This NBER data series m04137a appears on the NBER website in Chapter 4 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter04.html.
